des: 97.5 FM, KNMO \"Double K Country\" is a radio station located in Nevada, Missouri. It's a radio station that supports its community with local news, weather and sports coverage along with the best in country music. It serves a nine county area in west central and southwest Missouri along with southeast Kansas.
